{"descriptions":[{"id":1462,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe auxiliary \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡོད་\u003c/span\u003e is used with reference to habitual facts that involve the speaker:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eང་ན་གི་མེད།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;I\u0026rsquo;m never ill.\u0026rdquo; \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསྔན་མ་ང་ཡག་པོ་མཐོང་གི་ཡོད། \u003c/span\u003e\u0026ldquo;Previously, I used to see well.\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eངའི་བུ་མོ་སློབ་གྲྭ་ལ་འགྲོ་གི་ཡོད།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;My daughter goes to school.\u0026rdquo; \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཁོང་ངའི་ནང་ལ་ཡང་སེ་ཕེབས་ཀྱི་ཡོད། \u003c/span\u003e\u0026ldquo;He often comes to my place.\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:58 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:58 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}